block; line-height: 1.1; font-size: 13.6px; padding: 1px 4px 2px; background-color: rgb(27, 161, 226); border-radius: 2px; vertical-align: middle; cursor: pointer;\">Chuỗi JSON</a></li></ul><h1 style=\"border-collapse: collapse; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 2.25rem; line-height: 1.1; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif, serif; margin: 0.625rem 0px;\"><strong style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\"><span style=\"border-collapse: collapse; color: rgb(255, 140, 0);\">III. Lắp ráp phần cứng:</span></strong></h1><p style=\"border-collapse: collapse; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif, serif; font-size: 17px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Các bạn nối module 8 relay với mạch bSmart theo sơ đồ sau:</p><p class=\"rtecenter\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; text-align: center; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif, serif; font-size: 17px;\"><em style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\"><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/XvU2vhD.png\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; color: rgb(32, 134, 191);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XvU2vhD.png\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border: 2px solid; max-height: 100%; width: 383px;\"></a></em></p><p class=\"rtecenter\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; text-align: center; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif, serif; font-size: 17px;\"><em style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\">Sơ đồ kết nối 8 relay với bSmart, các bạn có thể chọn 8 chân khác nếu thích</em></p><h1 style=\"border-collapse: collapse; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 2.25rem; line-height: 1.1; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif, serif; margin: 0.625rem 0px;\"><span style=\"border-collapse: collapse; color: rgb(255, 140, 0);\"><strong style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\